    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>回忆中的声音挥之不去——你听见了吗？</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1683270/extras/8321e24b27c020d5f664f8adfce171e3.avif?t=1744089863\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1683270/extras_big/8321e24b27c020d5f664f8adfce171e3.avif?t=1744089863 width=800 height=370 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1683270/extras/8e67765486de31e37fffff9767da1d86.avif?t=1744089863\" width=610 height=110 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >聪明又善解人意的男孩林子维，为何会突然失踪？某天，林子晴找到了她和弟弟林子维童年的玩具话筒，这个神秘的话筒引导子晴与她的朋友一起进入虚幻的世界，在那里他们可以探索与子维相关人物的回忆。通过话筒穿梭在人物们最深层的愿望里，并藉此揭开子维失踪背后的真相。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家将扮演姐姐子晴与她的朋友睿萱，一起重温子维与生命中重要角色的回忆。每一章节都将深入探讨一个角色的过去，并揭示他们心中各自埋藏的愿望与秘密。在这个值得探索的2D横向卷轴游戏里，玩家可与角色互动、调查场景、收集物品并做出抉择，子维失踪的谜团就埋藏在其中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1683270/extras/82bf96536a4332a2a58c1520776e6076.poster.avif?t=1744089863\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1683270/extras/82bf96536a4332a2a58c1520776e6076.webm?t=1744089863\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1683270/extras/82bf96536a4332a2a58c1520776e6076.mp4?t=1744089863\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>▴五位主要角色，由右至左依序是：林子晴(姊姊)、黄咏英(姊弟的母亲)、林子维(弟弟)、何昱铭(子维同学)、简睿萱(子晴同学)</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1683270/extras/06345b661ff39aff919fb8dfa9f32330.poster.avif?t=1744089863\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1683270/extras/06345b661ff39aff919fb8dfa9f32330.webm?t=1744089863\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1683270/extras/06345b661ff39aff919fb8dfa9f32330.mp4?t=1744089863\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>▴回忆的世界――《遗望迴廊》</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1683270/extras/32b1962bfb0249c74eba4c6db890caab.avif?t=1744089863\" width=610 height=110 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >基于2010年代台湾学生文化的沉浸式冒险</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >非线性叙事结合幻想、悬疑与恐怖元素</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多重角色叙事，从不同视角探索整个故事</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择与行动将影响其他角色与结局分歧</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2D横向卷轴游戏玩法，富含互动元素和解谜</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >像素视觉风格与角色立绘相结合</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >支持多种语言，包括中文、英文及日文</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1683270/extras/b088d4042a4a4415b5d4059aaf9d1e40.poster.avif?t=1744089863\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1683270/extras/b088d4042a4a4415b5d4059aaf9d1e40.webm?t=1744089863\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1683270/extras/b088d4042a4a4415b5d4059aaf9d1e40.mp4?t=1744089863\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>▴与过去的影像互动、解谜</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1683270/extras/91d4e640e012788ea946e816f3106e18.poster.avif?t=1744089863\" width=610 height=298 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1683270/extras/91d4e640e012788ea946e816f3106e18.webm?t=1744089863\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1683270/extras/91d4e640e012788ea946e816f3106e18.mp4?t=1744089863\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>▴迴廊中的神祕電话亭</i></p>",
